# Grantify Academy Environment Variables

## Required Variables

VITE_SITE_URL=https://grantifyacademy.com

## Supabase (PostgreSQL)

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://vfwhismhogfzvbsznqts.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-supabase-anon-key-here

## Redis Cache

REDIS_HOST=185.230.64.89
REDIS_PORT=6379
REDIS_USERNAME=default
REDIS_PASSWORD=your-redis-password
REDIS_URL=redis://default:your-redis-password@185.230.64.89:6379
CACHE_TTL=300

## Mistral AI (for auto-fill features)

VITE_MISTRAL_API_KEY=your-mistral-api-key-here

## Database Connection (Alternative to Supabase)

# Uncomment if using backend API instead of Supabase directly
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api

## Feature Flags

VITE_USE_SUPABASE=true

## Security

# Consider setting a different default locale
# DEFAULT_LOCALE=ar

---

## Notes

- Replace all `YOUR-` placeholders with actual values from your environment
- Never commit `.env` files to version control - they're listed in .gitignore
- The site requires both Redis and either Supabase or a backend API to function properly
- For production, ensure all database credentials are properly secured
